{"id":71509,"title":"[Enriching patient care with aromatherapy].","abstract":"There are increasing numbers of initiatives in healthcare institutions focusing on the benefits of essential oils. Received positively by patients who appreciate the resulting wellbeing, these innovative approaches around aromatherapy are based on the initiative of pioneering caregivers. Following on from an international congress held each year in Grasse, this article presents some example schemes.","date":"2014-07-28","categories":"Neoplasms","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25065196","annotations":[{"name":"Health care","weight":0.431073,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_care"},{"name":"Aromatherapy","weight":0.0711346,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aromatherapy"},{"name":"United States Congress","weight":0.0332387,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States_Congress"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.0300804,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Quality of life","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quality_of_life"},{"name":"Follow-on","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Follow-on"},{"name":"Oil","weight":0.0157947,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oil"},{"name":"Grasse","weight":0.0148276,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grasse"},{"name":"Essential oil","weight":0.0148013,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Essential_oil"},{"name":"Initiative","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Initiative"},{"name":"Scheme (mathematics)","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scheme_(mathematics)"},{"name":"International","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International"},{"name":"Caregiver","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caregiver"}]}
